te to item":["P\u0159ej\u00edt na polo\u017eku"],"Preview your website's visual identity: colors, typography, and blocks.":["Prohl\u00e9dn\u011bte si vizu\u00e1ln\u00ed identitu sv\u00e9ho webu: barvy, typografii a bloky."],"Global Styles pagination":["Str\u00e1nkov\u00e1n\u00ed glob\u00e1ln\u00edch styl\u016f"],"Apply the selected revision to your site.":["Pou\u017e\u00edt vybranou revizi na web."],"Additionally, paragraphs help structure the flow of information and provide logical breaks between different concepts or pieces of information. In terms of formatting, paragraphs in websites are commonly denoted by a vertical gap or indentation between each block of text. This visual separation helps visually distinguish one paragraph from another, creating a clear and organized layout that guides the reader through the content smoothly.":["Odstavce nav\u00edc pom\u00e1haj\u00ed strukturovat tok informac\u00ed a vytv\u00e1\u0159ej\u00ed logick\u00e9 p\u0159ed\u011bly mezi r\u016fzn\u00fdmi pojmy nebo informacemi. Z hlediska form\u00e1tov\u00e1n\u00ed jsou odstavce na webov\u00fdch str\u00e1nk\u00e1ch obvykle ozna\u010deny svislou mezerou nebo odsazen\u00edm mezi ka\u017ed\u00fdm blokem textu. Toto vizu\u00e1ln\u00ed odd\u011blen\u00ed pom\u00e1h\u00e1 vizu\u00e1ln\u011b odli\u0161it jeden odstavec od druh\u00e9ho a vytv\u00e1\u0159\u00ed p\u0159ehledn\u00e9 a uspo\u0159\u00e1dan\u00e9 rozvr\u017een\u00ed, kter\u00e9 \u010dten\u00e1\u0159e plynn\u011b provede obsahem."],"A paragraph in a website refers to a distinct block of text that is used to present and organize information. It is a fundamental unit of content in web design and is typically composed of a group of related sentences or thoughts focused on a particular topic or idea. Paragraphs play a crucial role in improving the readability and user experience of a website. They break down the text into smaller, manageable chunks, allowing readers to scan the content more easily.":["Odstavec na webov\u00e9 str\u00e1nce ozna\u010duje samostatn\u00fd blok textu, kter\u00fd se pou\u017e\u00edv\u00e1 k prezentaci a organizaci informac\u00ed. Je to z\u00e1kladn\u00ed jednotka obsahu ve webov\u00e9m designu a obvykle se skl\u00e1d\u00e1 ze skupiny vz\u00e1jemn\u011b souvisej\u00edc\u00edch v\u011bt nebo my\u0161lenek zam\u011b\u0159en\u00fdch na konkr\u00e9tn\u00ed t\u00e9ma nebo n\u00e1pad. Odstavce hraj\u00ed kl\u00ed\u010dovou roli p\u0159i zlep\u0161ov\u00e1n\u00ed \u010ditelnosti a u\u017eivatelsk\u00e9ho z\u00e1\u017eitku z webu. Rozd\u011bluj\u00ed text na men\u0161\u00ed, snadno zvl\u00e1dnuteln\u00e9 \u010d\u00e1sti, co\u017e \u010dten\u00e1\u0159\u016fm umo\u017e\u0148uje snadn\u011bji prohled\u00e1vat obsah."],"AaBbCcDdEeFfGgHhIiJjKkLlMmNnOoPpQqRrSsTtUuVvWwXxYyZz0123456789X{(\u2026)},.-<>?!*&:\/A@HELFO\u2122\u00a9":["AaBbCcDdEeFfGgHhIiJjKkLlMmNnOoPpQqRrSsTtUuVvWwXxYyZz0123456789X{(\u2026)},.-<>?!*&:\/A@HELFO\u2122\u00a9"],"Default Gradients":["V\u00fdchoz\u00ed p\u0159echody"],"Default Colors":["V\u00fdchoz\u00ed barvy"],"Custom Gradients":["Vlastn\u00ed p\u0159echody"],"Theme Colors":["Barvy \u0161ablony"],"Theme Gradients":["P\u0159echody \u0161ablony"],"Duotones":["Dvout\u00f3ny"],"Are you sure you want to delete \"%s\" shadow preset?":["Opravdu chcete smazat p\u0159edvolbu st\u00ednu \\\"%s\\\"?"],"Remove all custom shadows":["Odebrat v\u0161echny vlastn\u00ed st\u00edny"],"Shadow options":["Mo\u017enosti st\u00ednu"],"Are you sure you want to remove all custom shadows?":["Opravdu chcete odebrat v\u0161echny vlastn\u00ed st\u00edny?"],"noun\u0004Upload":["Nahr\u00e1t"],"The theme you are currently using does not support this screen.":["Aktu\u00e1ln\u011b pou\u017e\u00edvan\u00fd motiv tuto obrazovku nepodporuje."],"Explore block styles and patterns to refine your site.":["Prozkoumejte styly blok\u016f a vzory pro zdokonalen\u00ed sv\u00e9ho webu."],"field\u0004Edit %s":["Upravit %s"],"taxonomy menu label\u0004%1$s (%2$s)":["%1$s (%2$s)"],"taxonomy template menu label\u0